<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Naluvenya on Vallon Zek</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-02-08 14:08:13</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>The ring is rechargable, like the one before me said.  The merchant has an "x" in her name, and she is located on the first floor.  Just hail every merchants.  HOWEVER, you need good faction with the necro guild ( TheDead ).  You can acheive that easily by completing the quest of the fire beetle eyes if you're a necro or SK.  If not, find one and ask him to recharge the ring for you. I'm not sure if with it non-pure spellcaster can bind themselves where they want but I really think they can't.  I'll try to do the quest and post another comment.</font></td></tr></table>
